{{/if}}

### Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} install
```

### Development

```bash
# Start development server
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run dev
```
{{#if docker.enabled}}

### Docker

```bash
# Start with Docker (development)
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run docker:dev

# Start with Docker (production)
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run docker:prod
```
{{/if}}

### Build

```bash
# Build all packages
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run build
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run tests
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run test

# Run tests with coverage
{{default packageManager 'bun'}} run test:coverage
```

